items.title: Magic number 2, Tribe can clinch AL Central
items.summary: The Indians, who already have secured a postseason berth, can clinch the American League Central title with a win on Saturday against the Royals and a loss by the Twins, who play the Blue Jays.

items.title: Cubs' Contreras suspended two games
items.summary: Chicago Cubs catcher Willson Contreras has received a two-game suspension and an undisclosed fine for his inappropriate actions -- which included the throwing of his mask, which contacted Umpire Jordan Baker -- in the top of the fifth inning of Friday's game against the St. Louis Cardinals at Wrigley Field.
items.content: Chicago Cubs catcher Willson Contreras has received a two-game suspension and an undisclosed fine for his inappropriate actions -- which included the throwing of his mask, which contacted Umpire Jordan Baker -- in the top of the fifth inning of Friday's game against the St. Louis Cardinals at Wrigley Field.
